_sText:
The map was designed to enhance the cs_ maps gaming experience. Every round is different and both sides can win, 
depending on the route that the team chooses to take.

Basically this is just an experimental map which i decited to share. I played too much wolf 3d at the other day and got too much influence from it. Map is large'ish but quick to dowload and has enough spawnpoints. Have fun.
